ited States more than 95 years ago are in the public domain in their entirety. Any newspapers in Chronicling America that were published less than 95 years ago are also believed to be in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.141635, "shard": "05", "shelf_id": "sn87057934, 1908-02-06, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/iahi", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["audubon", "exira", "newspapers", "iowa", "exira (iowa)", "united states"], "subject_headings": ["Exira (Iowa)--Newspapers", "Iowa--Exira", "United States--Iowa--Audubon--Exira"], "subjects": [{"audubon": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:audubon&fo=json"}, {"exira": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:exira&fo=json"}, {"exira (iowa)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:exira+%28iowa%29&fo=json"}, {"iowa": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:iowa&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2023-07-04T10:58:17.916Z", "title": "Audubon County journal (Exira, Iowa), February 6, 1908", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn87057934/1908-02-06/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn87057934/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn87057934"], "batch": ["iahi_jackson_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1884", "description": ["Weekly Began in Sept. 1884; ceased in 1993. Publisher varies. Issues lack numbering, <June 29, 1893-Dec. 25, 1919>. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Merged with: Audubon news-advocate; to form: Audubon County advocate journal. Description based on: June 29, 1893. Audubon news-advocate (DLC)sn 87057932 (OCoLC)16972871 Audubon County advocate journal 1071-7854 (DLC)sn 93005675 (OCoLC)28737032"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:11.942Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-12", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-12"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn87057934/", "image_url": [], "index": 1, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [41.591135, -94.885698], "location": ["audubon", "iowa", "exira", "united states"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-94.885698, 41.591135], "number": ["2025-06-25t14:24:16", "2024-05-12t17:17:02.191186", "crest microfilm, collection 1", "online resource", "16972906", "microfilm master", "sn87057932", "microfilm service copy", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn87057934/1897-01-28/ed-1/", "1291", "sn93005675", "2474-638x", "state hist soc of iowa, newspaper off", "sn87057934", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "1", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn87057934/1921-12-29/ed-1/"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "catalog", "serial and government publications division", "audubon county journal (exira, iowa) 1884-1993", "chronicling america"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 66.41939, "shelf_id": "Newspaper", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["audubon", "exira", "newspapers", "iowa", "exira (iowa)", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:22:49.039Z", "title": "Audubon County journal", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn87057934/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2016271199/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1884", "dates": ["[1884 TO 1993]"], "description": ["Weekly Began in Sept. 1884; ceased in 1993. Publisher varies: G.W. Guernsey, <June 29, 1893>. Issues lack numbering, <June 29, 1893-Dec. 25, 1919>. Merged with: Audubon news-advocate; to form: Audubon County advocate journal. Description based on: January 28, 1897; title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed October 12, 2016). Latest issue consulted: Vol. 36, no. 52 (December 29, 1921) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed October 12, 2016). Audubon news-advocate Audubon County advocate journal"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:36.478Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2016271199/", "image_url": [], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "location": ["audubon", "iowa", "exira", "united states"], "number": ["online resource", "2474-6398", "960464310", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2016271199"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "audubon county journal (exira, iowa) 1884-1993 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 57.212166, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["audubon", "exira", "newspapers", "iowa", "exira (iowa)", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:54:14.600Z", "title": "